ttyrec is a tty recorder. ttyplay is a tty player.

Installation:

  % make

or if your system is SVR4 system (Solaris etc.),

  % make CFLAGS=-DSVR4

Usage:

  % ttyrec
  (In the excuted shell, do whatever you want and exit)

  % ttyplay ttyrecord

Have fun!

-- Satoru Takabayashi <satoru@namazu.org>
